---
import BaseLayout from '../../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout title="About Us" description="Learn about EasyCalc: free, fast and precise online calculators for finance, dates and utilities.">
  <div class="static-page">
    <h1>About Us</h1>
    <p class="lead">EasyCalc was built with one simple goal: make everyday calculations accessible to everyone — no sign-up, no cost, no complexity.</p>
    <h2>What is EasyCalc?</h2>
    <p>We are a collection of free online tools that let you calculate percentages, discounts, loan payments, compound interest, date differences, timezone conversions, and more — directly in your browser, no installation needed.</p>
    <h2>Our mission</h2>
    <p>We believe everyone deserves access to clear, reliable financial and mathematical tools. Whether you're a student, a professional, an entrepreneur, or simply someone who wants to better understand their finances — EasyCalc is here to help.</p>
    <h2>How it works</h2>
    <p>All our calculators run directly on your device. We don't send your data to any external server. Results are instant.</p>
    <h2>Contact</h2>
    <p>Have a suggestion or found an error? Visit our <a href="/en/contact/">contact page</a>.</p>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
<style>
  .static-page { max-width: 760px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 2rem 0; }
  .static-page h1 { font-size: 2rem; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; }
  .static-page h2 { font-size: 1.3rem; margin: 2rem 0 .75rem; color: #1e3a8a; }
  .static-page p { color: #374151; line-height: 1.8; margin-bottom: 1rem; }
  .lead { font-size: 1.1rem; color: #4b5563; font-style: italic; }
</style>
